data.text:
Au secours du Capitaine ! (Help the Captain!) is the fourth French DVD release of PAW Patrol. It was released in France on August 19, 2015.

Summary

Pendant que le capitaine Turbot essaye de photographier l'oiseau aux pieds bleus, il tombe accidentellement à la mer et son bateau part à la dérive. Vite, c'est une mission pour la Pat' Patrouille ! Zuma part lui porter secours avec son aéroglisseur, Ryder se charge de reprendre les commandes du bateau et Stella s'envole pour retrouver l'oiseau. Aucune mission n'est trop dure car la Pat' Patrouille assure !

English translation: When Cap'n Turbot tries to photograph a blue-footed bird, he accidentally falls overboard and his boat drifts away. Now it's a mission for the PAW Patrol! Zuma lends a helping hand using his hovercraft, Ryder regains control of the boat, and Skye finds the bird. No mission is too difficult because the PAW Patrol ensures!

Episodes Included

Pups Save the Turbots

Pups Make a Splash

Pups in a Fog

Pups Save the Bay

Pups Save a Goodway

Pups Fall Festival

Pups Save a Toof
